title: Titles & Ranks
body:
Government

Mutasaih

  • Unäðem (Warden of the state)
  • Raksoþ (Head of the State Army)
  • Lietën (Principle advisor to the Unäðem)

Gorjovak

  • Cazar


Religious

Spiritual Temple

  • Ren-Ëðreso (Head of the Temple Collective)
  • Ren-Lutso (Prinicipal Representative of a Temple in the Temple Collective)
  • Ren-Sumbi (Head of a Temple)
  • Ren-Milleş (Principal Scholar of a Temple)
  • Templar (A religious person who lives in a Temple)
